      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Sune Fischer</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/sune-fischer-61b4197/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b1/SuneFischer.jpg/200px-SuneFischer.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b1/SuneFischer.jpg/300px-SuneFischer.jpg 1.5x, /images/b/b1/SuneFischer.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:SuneFischer.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Sune Fischer <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Sune Fischer</b>,<br />\na Danish physicist, computer scientist and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Solution_stack\">full-stack</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/.NET_Framework\">.NET</a> developer with experience and interests in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Solution_architecture\">solution architecture</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cloud_computing\">cloud computing</a>, \n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Software_quality\">code quality</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Agile_software_development\">agile processes</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Test_automation\">automated testing</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CI/CD\">CI\\CD</a>\\<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DevOps\">DevOps</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\nHe holds a Bachelor in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physics\">physics</a> in 2001 from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Copenhagen\">University of Copenhagen</a> on <a href=\"/Simulated_Annealing\" title=\"Simulated Annealing\">simulated annealing</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Travelling_salesman_problem\">travelling salesman problem</a>, covering <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Metropolis%E2%80%93Hastings_algorithm\">Metropolis–Hastings algorithm</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thermodynamics\">thermodynamics</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Statistical_mechanics\">statistical mechanics</a>, \nand further worked on <a href=\"/Neural_Networks\" title=\"Neural Networks\">neural networks</a>. As a chess player and computer chess programmer, Sune Fischer is author of the <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> and <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compatible chess engine <a href=\"/Frenzee\" title=\"Frenzee\">Frenzee</a>, previously known as <i>ChessCraft</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\nAlong with <a href=\"/Pradu_Kannan\" title=\"Pradu Kannan\">Pradu Kannan</a>, he contributed to the <a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Chess Programming Wiki</a> in 2007 with the examination on <a href=\"/Pawn_Advantage,_Win_Percentage,_and_Elo\" title=\"Pawn Advantage, Win Percentage, and Elo\">Pawn Advantage, Win Percentage, and Elo</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sune_Fischer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sune_Fischer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=183650\">The Alpha-Beta search!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 14, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Alpha-Beta\" title=\"Alpha-Beta\">Alpha-Beta</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=188901\">Move generation question for the big boys</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 15, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Generation\" title=\"Move Generation\">Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=194920\">Attack Bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 30, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Rotated_Bitboards\" title=\"Rotated Bitboards\">Rotated Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=203516\">When to RecordHash()?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 25, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2002</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=210339\">Reversed vs. Rotated Bitboards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 28, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Reverse_Bitboards\" title=\"Reverse Bitboards\">Reverse Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=238333\">Precomputed move information</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 02, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Table-driven_Move_Generation\" title=\"Table-driven Move Generation\">Table-driven Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=267805\">Book design</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 28, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Opening_Book\" title=\"Opening Book\">Opening Book</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2003</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=278587\">The Frenzee Report</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 21, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Frenzee\" title=\"Frenzee\">Frenzee</a>, <a href=\"/CCT5\" title=\"CCT5\">CCT5</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=280707\">Question about 50 move rule and e.p./castle flags</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 31, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Fifty-move_Rule\" title=\"Fifty-move Rule\">Fifty-move Rule</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=283426\">Unstable aspiration search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 10, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=287757\">One-reply extension howto</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 03, 2003&#160;»<a href=\"/One_Reply_Extensions\" title=\"One Reply Extensions\">One Reply Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=291062\">FirstOne for Linux</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 29, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/BitScan\" title=\"BitScan\">BitScan</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=308392\">Replacement shemes</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 27, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2004</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=388106\">Instability thing...</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 18, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/Triangular_PV-Table\" title=\"Triangular PV-Table\">Triangular PV-Table</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sune_Fischer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36569\">The grand design</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 01, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=37949\">Draft of Manifesto</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 05, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=58392&amp;start=47\">Re: Ugly UCI</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Sune Fischer</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 29, 2015</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sune_Fischer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/sune-fischer-61b4197/\">Sune Fischer | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=1413716\">Fischer, Sune FIDE Chess Profile</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sune_Fischer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/sune-fischer-61b4197/\">Sune Fischer | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/sune-fischer-61b4197/\">Sune Fischer | LinkedIn</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=36801&amp;start=4\">Re: KDL Chess released! + Update and new name for ChessCraft</a> by <a href=\"/Leo_Dijksman\" title=\"Leo Dijksman\">Leo Dijksman</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, April 10, 2002</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228225528\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.020 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.022 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 65/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 138/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion ti